      "rationale": "Fluent 2022R2 verified against Taylor-Couette flow and lid-driven cavity benchmarks. Rotating reference frame implementation confirmed against analytical solutions. Code verification at gradation 2 is satisfied for the hemolysis-relevant flow regime."
