      "rationale": "Three-level mesh refinement study performed: coarse (2.1M cells), medium (5.8M cells), fine (14.2M cells). GCI for NIH on fine grid = 3.1%, satisfying the acceptance criterion. Spatial order of convergence p = 1.94, consistent with second-order scheme."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Test conditions",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 2,
