      "rationale": "Validation performed on the FDA generic centrifugal pump, which shares impeller topology with the CPB device under assessment. Operating envelope (2–6 L/min, 2000–3500 RPM) fully encompasses CPB clinical range. Validation activities are judged sufficiently representative of the COU."
