      "rationale": "SST k-ω turbulence model selected based on published benchmarks for rotating blood-contacting devices. Giersiepen-Wurzinger power-law hemolysis model adopted per FDA guidance. Model form documented but formal assessment not required at MRL 2."
    },
    {
