    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required gradation levels for MRL 2. The six not-assessed factors are acceptable at MRL 2 per ASME V&V 40 Table 4. Uncertainty quantification via comprehensive Monte Carlo sampling across all model inputs confirms that the RH < 1 acceptance criterion is satisfied at the 95th percentile. The overall credibility evidence is sufficient to support the regulatory decision for this Class II CPB device.",
